AVSERVER(1m)	             USER COMMAND              AVSERVER(1m)

NAME
	avserver - send a request to the GEM desktop.

SYNOPSIS
	avserver <FILENAME>

	<FILENAME> filename to open.
	
DESCRIPTION
	This Mupfel script sends a AV_PROGSTART message to the
	AV-server. The environ variable AVSERVER should be
	defined. Typically this command is used to display a
	file content.

SEE ALSO
	applwrit, applfind, avserver, vastart.


